{"tid":2373493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"所謂嘅維基百科戰線 原來係幫對家","createTime":"2021-01-20T13:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T04:33:15.000Z","uid":10540,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ba81564228dad4a153e417467703195b9fdf9a72","tid":2373493,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:18:40.000Z","msg":"見到對家不斷就反修例合理使用圖片去提刪，想人哋去關注，原來維基戰線admin係唔容許，好快就刪咗唔想大家關注。而佢哋立場唔少竟然都係唔支持保留。<br />\n<br />\n到而家對家不斷大刪反修例運動主條目，想叫大家去關注，維基戰線admin都係會照刪，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">反映維基戰線根本有哂hidden agenda，任由對家不斷坐大</span></span>，成班人就當冇事發生過刻意唔理會，channel任務完全冇人理，真心好失望。<br />\n<br />\n自己花時間想更多人關注，佢哋就係擺明唔想大家關注，仲不斷洗白將問題合理化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P2LH2c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP2LH2c9.png&h=a2858ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjiVCMv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjiVCMv.png&h=5105f94e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">睇吓大家會唔會有意見，有就好出聲，唔好俾親中果班一言堂話哂事，繼續刪改真相！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A9%E5%AE%A2%E6%A0%88/%E6%9D%A1%E7%9B%AE%E6%8E%A2%E8%AE%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWikipedia%3A%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25A0%2588%2F%25E6%259D%25A1%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%258E%25A2%25E8%25AE%25A8&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=4e8bc227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A9%E5%AE%A2%E6%A0%88/%E6%9D%A1%E7%9B%AE%E6%8E%A2%E8%AE%A8</a>"},{"pid":"cef50c30085d7240e395a3a10656a8f65c79dbcb","tid":2373493,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:28:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"704db78868e80df92d2a9121d2ef9dbcf823473f","tid":2373493,"uid":45708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20