家係想逐一清除一d唔順眼、抵觸紅線嘅人，係中共常用手法。<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">結果大家都見到人哋不斷修改都選擇唔出聲當冇事，你選擇刪，即係唔想成1600人可以關注人地不斷無理刪改同不斷搬龍門。</span></span>"},{"pid":"1aee1082791ad8832f16e7c3f926e7fa84e43ecd","tid":2373493,"uid":28249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T23:26:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d70aca94db70c83fc8e4a6527bfe0e3e272f7b6","tid":2373493,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7d7506962150023b7e7997f8b0a8d209e8e3787a","tid":2373493,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T20:49:44.000Z","msg":"我喺另外兩個post有詳盡回應：<br />\n維基親中用戶陸續提出刪去反修例圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/rPonDcX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rPonDcX</a><br />\n<br />\n中文維基百科禁止使用西灣河開槍事件相<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/sbidqGX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/sbidqGX</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T01:02:29.000Z","msg":"我打咗咁多字，除咗負評之外你無其他回應？"},{"pid":"5c68eaaa81d2dfe6e7808b3b6ef334bd47f471ad","tid":2373493,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d70aca94db70c83fc8e4a6527bfe0e3e272f7b6","tid":2373493,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7d7506962150023b7e7997f8b0a8d209e8e3787a","tid":2373493,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T20:49:44.000Z","msg":"我喺另外兩個post有詳盡回應：<br />\n維基親中用戶陸續提出刪去反修例圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/rPonDcX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rPonDcX</a><br />\n<br />\n中文維基百科禁止使用西灣河開槍事件相<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/sbidqGX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/sbidqGX</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T01:02:29.000Z","msg":"我打咗咁多字，除咗負評之外你無其他回應？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:30:34.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇回應？"},{"pid":"983a8a725bb10f6feeffeab5fc878003e12add2c","tid":2373493,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T00:25:17.000Z","msg":"而家對家不斷靜悄悄去修改當睇唔到<br />\n封區咁大件事又可以冇人開條目<br />